title: Sharpe's.Eagle [2 of 15]
description:
[center][i][b]Sharpe's Eagle[/b][/i][/center]



[center]The newly promoted Captain Sharpe will be stripped of his rank unless he can 
save the honour of the regiment by capturing a French Imperial standard: an 
eagle.  Fast moving, hard-hitting action adventure filmed on location in the 
Crimea, Portugal and England brings to the screen all the danger, romance and 
sheer spectacle of one of the bloodiest periods in English warfare. 

Cast: 
Sean Bean as Lt. Richard Sharpe
Brian Cox as Major Hogan
Daragh O'Malley as Sgt. Patrick Harper
Assumpta Serna as Teresa Moreno
David Troughton asGeneral Sir Arthur Wellesley [/center]
